<td style="text-align:center; background: #ccf;"><b>Books</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: center;"><i><a href="/wiki/Tokyo_(novel)" title="Tokyo (novel)">Tokyo</a></i> (2004)<br />
