<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b>
<blockquote class="templatequote">
<div>
<p>"The Japanese Army, one million strong, has already conquered <a href="/wiki/Changshu" title="Changshu">Changshu</a>. We have surrounded the city of Nanking… The Japanese Army shall show no mercy toward those who offer resistance, treating them with extreme severity, but shall harm neither innocent civilians nor Chinese military [personnel] who manifest no hostility. It is our earnest desire to preserve the East Asian culture. If your troops continue to fight, war in Nanking is inevitable. The culture that has endured for a millennium will be reduced to ashes, and the government that has lasted for a decade will vanish into thin air. This commander-in-chief issues [b]ills to your troops on behalf of the Japanese Army. Open the gates to Nanking in a peaceful manner, and obey the [f]ollowing instructions."</p>
</div>
</blockquote>
</li>
